{"tid":1197195,"cid":1,"subCid":0,"title":"How riot police works 警察防暴策略簡介","createTime":"2019-06-10T02:22:04.000Z","updateTime":"2019-07-30T01:11:11.000Z","uid":164402,"like":6,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":3,"replies":[{"pid":"fb354ced3f04083ed388bea280f65e44637fa46b","tid":1197195,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T02:22:04.000Z","msg":"要贏任何仗，其中一樣要素就係了解敵人強弱同策略（Know you enemy） <br />\n防暴警察數量唔夠示威者多，不能以一敵百，主要係會用以下方式控制示威者/令示威者覺得唔夠打（心理戰）：<br />\n<br />\n- 全身黑色裝備，包括頭盔，以黑色向示威者暗示權力， 自己亦感覺更強: &ldquo;穿上深色制服，感覺更安全了。感覺和現實一樣重要&rdquo;<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/eW9wH3u.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FeW9wH3u.jpg&h=09c10be7&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- 一字排開，揮動警棍(60-107 cm)，試圖嚇走無裝備示威者<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/oFWZRU3.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FoFWZRU3.jpg&h=ce0bf180&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n- Tear gas用途：令示威者要照顧自身安全，失去群眾行動力(mob mentality)<br />\n當一班人同時去做一樣野，會有無形壓力令其他人加入，打散咗就好易失去戰鬥力<br />\n<br />\n- 事實上，警察只有一個目標(ultimate goal)：就係令示威者離開/番屋企。<br />\n佢地永遠會留條路比啲唔想繼續參與既人走，當人數逐漸減少（香港人最鍾意番工，少人過夜），示威者就會失去最大既武器，去到得番幾百人警察就會包圍餘下示威者，示威/riot就會結束。<br />\n<br />\n當示威者人數眾多， 警察只能一字排開防守:<br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/6OUMwUk.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F6OUMwUk.jpg&h=8482a085&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n人數減少， 示威者被警察包圍:  <br />\n<img src=\"https://na.cx/i/xfBCDzq.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2FxfBCDzq.jpg&h=234a3536&s={SIZE}\" /> <br />\n只有香港人團結才能戰勝!<br />\n<br />\n另外，請帶足夠裝備:<br />\n  <img src=\"https://na.cx/i/2NEs0Nd.png\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Fna.cx%2Fi%2F2NEs0Nd.png&h=c0f2a13a&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\nSource: Riot control philosophy， The psychological influence of the police uniform, Egyptian Activists&rsquo; Action Plan"},{"pid":"e35c6119d9d4f8aeb25d9f60b83f9a5d1fa04da6","tid":1197195,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T04:51:04.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"f0c0e51b2c9602a21b2d2032c04f457ddce9ec01","tid":1197195,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:29:52.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"cfefa19b83406954fbb81f6737643cd78933efb2","tid":1197195,"uid":164402,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T05:37:55.000Z","msg":"推"},{"pid":"e2fa2723b33852e4c5c591fadde3c8276a8e0c4b","tid":1197195,"uid":82883,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-10T06:57:59.000Z","msg":"☝🏽"},{"pid":"9172181b739df479ea41c8f241fc41e638ca3566","tid":1197195,"uid":263577,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-07-30T01:11:11.000Z","msg":"推"}]}